1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,815
Independence and Education
独立和教育

2
00:00:06,253 --> 00:00:10,196
Young Nirmala was also seized with Nationalist zeal
年轻的涅玛拉也受民族主义热情支配 

3
00:00:10,696 --> 00:00:12,781
She was always extremely energetic
她总是极其精力旺盛

4
00:00:12,990 --> 00:00:15,835
And was a natural leader among her peers
是同龄人中自发公认的领袖

5
00:00:16,335 --> 00:00:19,427
In 1942 during the Quit India movement
在1942年‘退出印度’运动期间

6
00:00:19,574 --> 00:00:23,269
She participated in many daring episode of picketing
她参加与了许多英勇的游行示威

7
00:00:23,311 --> 00:00:27,109
and was also part of an underground group that carried out many secret missions
同时也是执行秘密任务的地下组织成员

8
00:00:27,734 --> 00:00:32,158
Because we were all college students
因为我们全是大学生

9
00:00:32,222 --> 00:00:35,233
We all wanted to stop the colleges
我们都想停止学业

10
00:00:35,733 --> 00:00:41,573
Then somehow or other we got into another kind of mysterious acting
然后我们设法参与了另一种秘密活动

11
00:00:41,655 --> 00:00:48,761
to distribute bulletins, used to call them bullets
发传单 我们叫它们子弹

12
00:00:49,261 --> 00:00:54,479
And spread disorder among students
在学生中产生骚乱

13
00:00:55,373 --> 00:00:57,794
That time students were very alert
那时侯学生们非常警醒

14
00:00:58,605 --> 00:01:00,814
that we should have our independence
我们应该有自主权

15
00:01:01,418 --> 00:01:03,060
We should be a free country
我们应该生活在一个自由的国家

16
00:01:03,705 --> 00:01:07,581
and people were not so dishonest as they are now
那时候人们不像现在这样不诚实

17
00:01:09,741 --> 00:01:13,135
After that I joined science college
之后，我加入科学院

18
00:01:13,988 --> 00:01:16,366
Because I wanted to do medicine
因为我想去学医学

19
00:01:17,468 --> 00:01:22,205
But science college we had a strike
但在科学院我组织了罢课

20
00:01:22,975 --> 00:01:25,886
And I became the leader of students
我成了学生领袖

21
00:01:26,926 --> 00:01:29,848
So they asked me to get out of the college
所以他们让我离开学校

22
00:01:30,722 --> 00:01:32,243
So I had to leave the college
所以我不得不离开学校

23
00:01:33,594 --> 00:01:36,178
Then I went to Lucknow to study
接着我去了勒克瑙学习

24
00:01:36,678 --> 00:01:40,568
in Ludhiana Women college that's also another missionary
在卢迪亚纳女子学院 也是一个教会学校

25
00:01:41,877 --> 00:01:44,570
But from there I did my science 
但在那里我修习了我的科学课程

26
00:01:45,672 --> 00:01:49,428
And then I did My Medicine from Lahore 
后来我在拉合尔学习医学
